Package org.wikipedia.miner.model

Class Summary
Anchor This class represents a term or phrase that is used to link to pages in Wikipedia.
Article This class represents articles in Wikipedia; the pages that contain descriptive text regarding a particular topic.
Category This class represents categories in Wikipedia; the pages that exist to organize articles that discuss related topics.
Disambiguation This class represents disambiguation pages in Wikipedia; the pages that list the various articles that an ambiguous term may refer to.
Page This class provides properties and methods that are relevant for all pages in Wikipedia.
Redirect This class represents redirects in Wikipedia; the links that have been defined to connect synonyms to the correct article (i.e Farming redirects to Agriculture).
SensePage This class represents an entry in a disambiguation page: a sense for which the
Wikipedia This class serves as the main portal into a Wikipedia database, and is intended to provide convenient methods for analysing it's content.
WikipediaDatabase This class loads, provides access to and maintains the Wikipedia database.
